

PALAGAY

   root word: lagay
   palagay
   opinion, judgment

   Ano sa palagay mo?
   What do you think?
   = What’s your take on it?
   = How do you see it?

   Sa palagay ko, tama ka.
   In my opinion, you are right.

   Bakit, sa palagay mo?
   Why, do you think?

   Bakit ganyan ang palagay mo?
   “Why do you think that way?”
   = Why do you think so?
